OL,3,CK-pop stars BTS perform live for first
OL,4,Ctime in four years
OL,6,FThousands of fans of the K-pop group
OL,7,FBTS gathered in South Korea for their
OL,8,Fcomeback show, as ITV News Reporter
OL,9,FWill Tullis explains
OL,11,FK-pop boyband BTS have returned to the
OL,12,Fstage for the first time in four years
OL,13,Fwith a performance at Gwanghwamun
OL,14,FSquare in Seoul.
OL,16,FSaturday's concert, which was streamed
OL,17,Flive on Netflix, saw the group perform
OL,18,Ftheir fifth studio album ` Arirang `
OL,19,Fthe day after its release, as well as
OL,20,Fsome of their biggest hits including
OL,21,FDynamite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
