OL,3,CK-pop stars BTS perform live for first
OL,4,Ctime in four years
OL,6,FThe group ` RM, Jin, Suga, J-hope,
OL,7,FJimin, V and Jung Kook ` went on
OL,8,Fhiatus in 2022, during which they
OL,9,Fcompleted mandatory military service
OL,10,Fin their home country.
OL,12,FIn a trailer for the concert, rapper
OL,13,FRM, real name Kim Nam-joon, says: "We
OL,14,Fpromised our fans that we would be
OL,15,Fback."
OL,26,@uD@cOUwD@FO]
