OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774224184
OL,3,CK-pop stars BTS perform live for first
OL,4,Ctime in four years
OL,6,FThe band gathered at the historic
OL,7,FGwanghwamun, the main gate of the
OL,8,FGyeongbokgung palace in Seoul, which
OL,9,Fwas lit up with purple, red and blue
OL,10,Fand filled with tens of thousands of
OL,11,Fscreaming fans.
OL,13,FDuring the hour-long show, Kim Seok-
OL,14,Fjin, who performs under the name Jin,
OL,15,Fsaid in Korean: "Thank you so much for
OL,16,Fcoming here. I had so many worries
OL,17,Fbefore about standing here today but
OL,18,Fseeing you all again, I'm so emotional
OL,19,Fand happy."
OL,26,@wD@QOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
