OL,3,CK-pop stars BTS perform live for first
OL,4,Ctime in four years
OL,6,FAddressing BTS's fanbase, named Army,
OL,7,Fhe said: "Thank you, Army."
OL,9,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FPark Ji-min, known as Jimin to fans,
OL,15,Falso addressed the crowd during the
OL,16,Fconcert and said: "We are finally here
OL,17,Fand seeing you again. The fact that I
OL,18,Fam speaking here... I am so moved.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@[O]xD@SOU
