OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774224184
OL,3,CK-pop stars BTS perform live for first
OL,4,Ctime in four years
OL,6,F"All seven of us standing on stage
OL,7,Ftogether makes me so happy. Thank you
OL,8,Fall so much. You have filled
OL,9,FGwanghwamun Square today."
OL,11,FThe group also thanked their fans
OL,12,Fthroughout the performance for waiting
OL,13,Ffor their return, and said that
OL,14,Freuniting on stage was a "dream".
OL,16,FIt has been reported that the group's
OL,17,Fleader RM injured himself prior to the
OL,18,Fperformance, and he was seen limiting
OL,19,Fhis movement and sitting on a chair at
OL,20,Ftimes throughout the show.
