OL,3,CK-pop stars BTS perform live for first
OL,4,Ctime in four years
OL,6,FFree tickets for the concert were
OL,7,Fallocated to fans through a global
OL,8,Flottery held on South Korean fan-
OL,9,Fcommunity website Weverse.
OL,11,FThe concert, which was streamed live
OL,12,Fon Netflix, comes ahead of the release
OL,13,Fof a new documentary in the streamer
OL,14,Ftitled BTS: The Return, which will be
OL,15,Freleased on March 21.
OL,17,FBTS ` an acronym of Bangtan
OL,18,FSonyeondan, or Beyond the Scene ` have
OL,19,Fhad four top 10 singles and two number
OL,20,Fone albums in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
