OL,3,CK-pop stars BTS perform live for first
OL,4,Ctime in four years
OL,6,FThey are best known in the UK for
OL,7,Fsongs such as Butter, Dynamite and
OL,8,FLife Goes On ` as well as
OL,9,Fcollaborations with western artists
OL,10,Fsuch as Charli XCX, Coldplay and
OL,11,FHalsey.
OL,13,FBTS were the first K-pop act to score
OL,14,Fa Grammy nomination.
OL,16,FThey are the best-selling music act in
OL,17,FSouth Korean history, having sold more
OL,18,Fthan 40 million albums, and the first
OL,19,Fnon-English speaking group to sell out
OL,20,FWembley Stadium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
